data.description: Sitting high atop a hill within the prestigious confines of Highland Estates, a luxurious home stands as a testament to architectural finesse and interior design mastery.  This residence, sprawling over two thirds of an acre of meticulously landscaped grounds, offers an unparalleled living experience, seamlessly blending opulence with comfort.  As we take you through this magnificent property, prepare to be captivated by its array of impressive features and bespoke details.  Upon arrival, the circular drive sets a tone of grandeur, leading up to an entrance that promises an interior as breathtaking as its facade.  The home is not just a marvel of design but also thoughtfully wheelchair accessible, ensuring inclusivity in its luxurious embrace.  Stepping inside, one is immediately struck by the expansive views offered by the backyard and patio.  As day turns to night, these sweeping vistas transform into a mesmerizing spectacle, with the twinkling lights of Kinder Ranch and beyond laid out in a panoramic display.  It's a view that invites contemplation and relaxation, best enjoyed from the comfort of the covered patio.  Here, an extended deck and privacy extensions create an intimate outdoor haven, perfect for entertaining or quiet evenings under the stars.  The interior of the home is a masterclass in luxury design, featuring designer fixtures that punctuate every room with a touch of elegance.  As you explore the home, the kitchen emerges as a culinary masterpiece, blending functionality with unrivaled elegance.  Granite countertops illuminate under the recessed and pendant lighting, providing ample space for preparation, while an expansive island invites communal cooking and conversation.  State-of-the-art appliances integrate seamlessly into custom cabinetry, reflecting a marriage of sophistication and practicality.  A simple white tile backsplash adds a layer of artistic flair, complemented by a walk-in pantry that ensures seamless organization. Just around the corner, the kitchen extends into a bar area, featuring matching granite counters, an ice maker, wine cooler, and additional cabinets.  This space is further enhanced with a built-in wine rack and glass storage, crafting an enclave perfect for uncorking some of your favorite vintages.  The primary bedroom, a serene retreat, boasts stained concrete floors that lend an edgy sophistication, complemented by a smeared brick wall that adds texture and character.  This room, like the rest of the house, benefits from thoughtful details that elevate the living experience.  Adjacent to this sanctuary, the primary bathroom continues the theme of understated luxury with its designer fixtures, central chandelier,  and detailed tile floor, creating a cohesive aesthetic that is both modern and timeless.  A secondary bedroom located downstairs offers versatility and convenience, serving as a perfect guest suite with its own private full bathroom.  The heart of the home, however, might just be the game room.  Here, a fantastic wood beam ceiling draws the eye upwards, adding a dramatic flair to the space.  It's a room designed for enjoyment and relaxation, from watching the game on a Sunday afternoon to a quiet night of movies and popcorn.  For the automobile enthusiast or hobbyist, the garage is a dream come true.  Equipped with a mini-split system for temperature control and stained flooring for durability, it goes beyond a place to park cars - it's a functional space for just about anything you desire.  In every detail, from the luxurious fixtures to the unique design elements, this home in Highland Estates is a masterpiece of interior design and architecture.
